to intall virtualbox in ubutnu--> sudo apt-get install virtualbox 

to download fedora image--> go to fedora.org link-->from "Workstation" download 64 bit live image. from the rigth corner.

then open virtual box and and create new then keep all the option as default they have mentioned...->>

then fedora image will be get created in virtualbox.

now click on that image and go to setting-->storage-->empty var click-->and give path of your iso image.
